version_description:
Cash Out is here! Now you can settle a bet before your game ends to either lock in winnings or cut your losses. With Cash Out the ball is in your court.

We have also improved the speed of bet placement for single/straight bets by introducing a “Fast” bet option on mobile, as well as enhanced the Parlay building experience by showing you how much you can win as you add selections

We’re always working on improving your Sportsbook experience. With this release, we’re making login easier by adding the following features.
- Face ID
- Touch ID

Plus, we’ve read your feedback and will continuously release updates and bug fixes. We always recommend you keep your app updated!

v1.2.0
- Bug fixes
